{"tid":1587754,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)白事可樂 霧地異煞 白宮又爆炸","createTime":"2019-09-22T14:09:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-22T18:27:52.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a27a1ea794653918fb6678efdb743e0e29e4dc44","tid":1587754,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T14:09:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=AaXh75k8ef15jyN5JBlvBlDHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=a16abef4\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=AaXh75k8ef15jyN5JBlvBlDHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=3755f36d\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=AaXh75k8ef15jyN5JBlvBlDHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=5a6ee8f0\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;&lt; GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/9/9f/Newworldwarzpostersmall.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F9%2F9f%2FNewworldwarzpostersmall.jpg&h=c21a4019&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/a/a1/The_Mist_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fa%2Fa1%2FThe_Mist_poster.jpg&h=28c6da5c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/5/5d/White_House_Down_poster_with_billing_block.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fen%2F5%2F5d%2FWhite_House_Down_poster_with_billing_block.jpg&h=0de00aa8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.前聯合國調查員傑瑞&middot;藍恩與自己的妻子凱倫和兩個女兒瑞秋與康妮，愉快的在擁擠的費城市區公路上行車，但一分鐘內就有多架直升機從空中飛過，而新聞上一直在談論關於台灣爆發的狂犬病毒。突然間，公路前方發生了爆炸，而公路上執勤的警察當場被失控的垃圾車撞死，傑瑞跟隨垃圾車的行進路線離開公路，之後與一輛失控的救護車發生相撞。傑瑞與凱倫回過神來後，帶著女兒們丟下汽車逃跑，而廣場上也轉眼間出現了幾百名瘋狂咬人的殭屍，而傑瑞與家人逃離時親眼看到一名被殭屍咬到的人，在十二秒之內也淪為了一個殭屍，後來與家人開著一輛房車逃離了城市。不到兩小時，費城淪陷，美軍阻止殭屍的軍事行動全部以失敗告終...<br />\n<br />\n2.一場暴風雨，鄰居諾頓律師的樹木倒塌，打壞電影海報畫家大衛德雷頓（湯瑪斯&middot;傑恩飾）的畫室，大衛和他的妻子看見不尋常的霧開始從山間蔓延，全鎮亦斷電。為重整風暴摧殘後的家園，大衛和5歲的兒子比利（納桑&middot;蓋博飾），與鄰居諾頓（安德魯&middot;布瑞格飾）去當地的超市採賣物品。到了店內，越來越多的警車在街上奔馳，引起顧客注意，最終空襲警報響起，一名老人丹米勒（傑佛瑞&middot;狄蒙飾）滿面鮮血，狼狽的跑進超市，警告大家有迎面而來的濃霧中有異物，非常駭人<br />\n<br />\n3.宣揚和平主義的美國總統詹姆士&middot;索耶爲了結束長久以來的中東戰爭而親自前往伊朗表示和平，聲言他會把所有部署在中東地區的美軍全部撤出，將自己的提案交給其他國家審核。約翰&middot;凱爾是一名在阿富汗服過兵役的美軍中士，因爲行爲不檢被革除後去當國會警察，成為美國眾議院議長伊萊&middot;拉弗森的私人護衛。而約翰好不容易得到一次美國特勤局的面試機會，並與自己關係不好的女兒愛蜜莉一同前去白宮。面試時，特勤隊副主任卡蘿&middot;菲妮提因為看不上約翰的狼藉簡歷而拒絕了他<br />\n<br />\n10 30PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=AaXh75k8ef15jyN5JBlvBlDHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=44bbf3f8\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=AaXh75k8ef15jyN5JBlvBlDHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=f2828945\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ce7821f26138ef5e3fcab93336a55b8f9664d36","tid":1587754,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T14:11:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3a34cf4e9cfda706d0df85c06ea525942ccce927","tid":1587754,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T14:11:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe7f13e0388a614204a210244ed0d51f9130ac6e","tid":1587754,"uid":149844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T14:13:22.000Z","msg":"白事有可樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ba55a876167dae7804472256a4373791f748a69","tid":1587754,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T14:37:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">Brexit都係靠呢招食糊！</span><br />\n【眾籌 Youtube 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dRrFcS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dRrFcS</a>"},{"pid":"1fd608975fdd7b1dd089698f579cea93194ee8d0","tid":1587754,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T15:43:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a51b12e1a195b5151277eec61d29b281aef4104","tid":1587754,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T17:19:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><im